<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Sandstone Valley</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A typical Calgary suburb in the North West, the Sandstone Valley is a low-density residential community that offers a quiet and relaxing haven for young couples, growing families and retirees alike.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">The Sandstone Real estate also offers its residents a good number of playing fields and beautiful parks in addition to a high-profile golf course and a state-of-the-art recreational fitness facility called Cardel Place.</p>

